          <p>8. SECURITY OF YOUR PERSONAL DATA. We are committed to protecting the security of your Personal Data. We use a variety of industry-standard security technologies and procedures to help protect your Personal Data from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. We also require you to enter a password to access your account information. Please do not disclose your account password to unauthorized people. Despite these measures, you should know that we cannot fully eliminate security risks associated with Personal Data and mistakes may happen.</p>

